This file is the decision ledger — the rationale and roads not taken, never rewritten. Every non-obvious choice is an ADR here, numbered and appended in order. It replaces what would be unretrievable history: the "why" behind the sealed spec, the toolchain pin, the context-chain architecture, the cage's isolation model, the leaf-summary style, and the pivot away from enforcement to injection. Status updates live in STATUS.md; this is decisions only.